"""
mlm-memory-extended — Layer 4–7 extension for gs-ai/mlm-memory
================================================================
Adds to the existing mlm-memory CLI:
  • preflight   — validate model fit BEFORE loading (saves OOM crashes)
  • recommend   — hardware-aware model recommender with MLA/SSM awareness
  • monitor     — real-time memory pressure display during a run
  • context-fit — dynamic Layer 4 context window optimizer

Drop this file next to the existing `mlm-memory` script and run:
  ./mlm-memory-extended preflight --model qwen2.5:14b
  ./mlm-memory-extended recommend
  ./mlm-memory-extended monitor
  ./mlm-memory-extended context-fit --model deepseek-r1:14b --target 0.85

Requirements: Python 3.9+  |  No extra dependencies beyond stdlib
Compatible with: mlm-memory repo as of 2026-03-19
"""

